<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>keep in mind...</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Seoman Snowlock">Seoman Snowlock</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 10:10 p.m. 1/4/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> keep in mind...<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=1846" TARGET=_self>Statistics on Root wanted</A> (TheBlack)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>that each class that gets the root style spell (grasping roots at first for Druids) gets improved versions as they rise in level. Ensnaring root for Druids at 19, then a new one at 29 or 34 I can't remember which...etc.

<P>Seo
<BR>ps: This also goes for Wizards..
<P>&gt; It appears that the spell Root becomes less and less effective
<BR>&gt; as you raise in level. I would like to confirm this with as much
<BR>&gt; data as can be gathered. Please run some tests and post the
<BR>&gt; results here. Note your level, your target's level, and the
<BR>&gt; results of each cast (resisted vs partial root vs full root).
<BR>&gt; The tests I did on casting root at lower levels showed the spell
<BR>&gt; working about 80% of the time vs a player 1 level higher than
<BR>&gt; the caster, with a full root lasting about 30 seconds and a
<BR>&gt; partial root about 6 seconds. Please cast the spell at least 10
<BR>&gt; times against the same target, asany fewer attempts won't
<BR>&gt; adequately measure the problem. Finally note your target's magic
<BR>&gt; resistance numbers so we can determine if they effect the
<BR>&gt; percentage of partial and fullly resisted roots.
<P>&gt; I am of the opnion that this spell should continue to function
<BR>&gt; in a predictable fashion through higher levels of ability. I'm
<BR>&gt; looking forward to seeing the results of this test. Feel free to
<BR>&gt; test other spells as well if you have the time.
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
<P ALIGN=CENTER><EM><A HREF="http://www.covetouscrew.org" TARGET=_top>CC</A></EM></P>
